pSnapshot","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshot","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNPolyline","kind":"symbol","iden